**Architecture concerns:**\n- None. The implementation follows established patterns exactly (filesystem fixtures, vi.mock for subprocess, switch-based format dispatch).\n\n**Items sent back for re-development:**\n- None. All HIGH and MEDIUM issues fixed. Story moved to `verifying`."}],"totalDurationMs":351339,"totalTokens":63772,"totalToolUseCount":54,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":783,"cache_read_input_tokens":62345,"output_tokens":643,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":783},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
